title: Orhan Taşdelen
text:
Orhan Tasdelen (born 6 February 1987) is a Turkish professional <a href="Association%20football">footballer</a> who plays as a <a href="defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> for <a href="24%20Erzincanspor">24 Erzincanspor</a>.
Professional career.
On 10 May 2018, Orhan helped <a href="Akhisar%20Belediyespor">Akhisar Belediyespor</a> win their first professional trophy, the <a href="2017%E2%80%9318%20Turkish%20Cup">2017–18 Turkish Cup</a>.
